BLACK MARKET: Knowing the illegal trade

Category: Trade
Base skill: 20% (+4%/level, cap 98%)

Knowing where illegal and hard-to-find goods actually change hands:
which contacts to trust, how a black market deal is supposed to go,
and what a fair (if unlawful) price looks like. Common in Splynn's
Dimensional Market and any Coalition-adjacent black market trade.

NOTES:
  No AetherMUD command currently rolls this skill directly. It is
  available for character concept and staff-adjudicated roleplay.

SEE ALSO: skills, barter, streetwise
